- Catalysts cross-referenced against the thesis files (SpaceX IPO, Quantinuum IPO, AVGO/PANW/CRWD earnings cluster next week, Jun 16–26 Triple Witch/FOMC convergence from CALENDAR.md).

No fabrication, no WebSearch used.
